The BambooHR app lets you take some of those most important functions with you, and makes your most common tasks in BambooHR simple and fast.

* In order to do anything with the BambooHR app you will need a current BambooHR account. Find out more on our website.
* The app fully supports single sign-on (SAML) to login

Your Company Directory, Everywhere You Go

Your company’s phone numbers, emails, photos, titles—your whole company directory goes wherever you do. 

* See colleague’s information and call, email, or message them with a tap
* Quickly add someone’s info to your phone’s contacts

Plan and Manage Time Off

Planning a trip? Request time off when you’re out and about. Leave requests can be submitted in the app, and if you’re an approver, you can approve them there as well.

* See who’s out of the office today and on any future date
* See current and calculate your future time off balances
* Submit, view, edit, and comment on your time off requests
* Approve and deny time off requests
* Push notifications keep you in the loop on the status of your requests

And don’t worry, TouchID and passcode protection will help keep your information secure.
